OL,3,CMan suffers gunshot wound to leg in
OL,4,Cearly morning shooting
OL,6,FA man has been taken to hospital
OL,7,Ffollowing an early morning shooting.
OL,9,FPolice were called to Boode Croft in
OL,10,FStockbridge Village, Knowsley, at
OL,11,Fapproximately 7.20am, on Thursday, 26
OL,12,FMarch, following reports of a firearms
OL,13,Fdischarge.
OL,15,FOfficers discovered a victim, believed
OL,16,Fto be a man in his 30s, who had
OL,17,Fsustained a gunshot wound to his leg.
OL,19,FHe was transported to hospital for
OL,20,Ftreatment, a spokesperson from
OL,21,FMerseyside Police said.
