OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774523168
OL,3,CMan suffers gunshot wound to leg in
OL,4,Cearly morning shooting
OL,6,FA significant police presence remains
OL,7,Fat the scene and a cordon has been
OL,8,Festablished to allow specialist
OL,9,Fofficers to carry out the early stages
OL,10,Fof a forensic investigation.
OL,12,FDetectives have confirmed they are
OL,13,Fconducting house-to-house enquiries to
OL,14,Fidentify witnesses and analysing CCTV
OL,15,Ffrom the surrounding area.
OL,17,FThey are urging anyone who was in the
OL,18,Fvicinity of Stockbridge Village at the
OL,19,Ftime of the shooting and saw anything
OL,20,Fsuspicious to come forward.
